title: Raan Thummachat
description: Vegetarian restaurant serving Thai fast food.  Owner speaks English. Note that signage is in Thai only. Directions: from Pattaya Klang rd turn north onto Paniad Chang Rd which runs along the east side of Big C extra, the restaurant is 1.3 km from the turn, about 6 shops north of the intersection that divides Paniad Chang Soi 3 on your left and Sukhumvit 34 Alley on your right - no sign marking the intersection so look for the Tantrarak school sign.
streetAddress: 388/84-85 Paniad Chang Rd, T Naklua, Banglamung
